---
const imgSrc = "/assets/home/secure-trading.png";
---

<div class="home secure trading">
  <div class="img">
    <img src={imgSrc} alt="Secure Trading" />
  </div>

  <div class="text">
    <p class="heading">Secure Trading for Everyone</p>

    <div class="description">
      <p>
        <span>No Registration.</span> We value your privacy and security! Skip registering
        with your personal info and engage with the crypto market anonymously.
      </p>

      <p>
        <span>No Intermediaries.</span> Experience the true power of decentralization—trade
        directly without involving intermediaries, enhancing security, transparency,
        and efficiency.
      </p>

      <p>
        <span>No Deposits.</span> We don't take custody of your funds. You maintain 
        full ownership of your funds, while we ensure your peace of mind and security.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
